<div id="Description">
<table cellpadding="0" cellspacing="0" border="0" width="100%" class="main">
<tr>
<td valign="top" class="NAME">&lt;jsp:param&gt;</td>
<td valign="top" class="COMPATIBILITY">&nbsp;</td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td colspan="2" class="divider"><img src="dwres:18084" width="100%" height="1"></td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td valign="top" colspan="2" class="description">


<p>Vous pouvez utiliser l'action <span class="LITERAL">&lt;jsp:param&gt;</span> dans le corps d'une action <span class="LITERAL">&lt;jsp:forward&gt;</span> ou <span class="LITERAL">&lt;jsp:include&gt;</span> pour sp&eacute;cifier des param&egrave;tres de demande suppl&eacute;mentaires pour la ressource cible, ainsi que dans le corps d'une action <span class="LITERAL">&lt;jsp:params&gt;</span> pour sp&eacute;cifier des param&egrave;tres d'applet.
</p>
<p>Exemple&nbsp;:</p>

<span class="PROGRAMLISTING"><pre>&lt;jsp:include page=&quot;navigation.jsp&quot;&gt;
  <strong class="userinput">&lt;jsp:param name=&quot;bgColor&quot; value=&quot;&lt;%= currentBGColor %&gt;&quot;</strong>
<strong class="userinput">    /&gt;</strong>
&lt;/jsp:include&gt;</pre></span>

</td></tr>
</table>
</div>

